genresAdvancedInfo.name: new hampshire indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: New Hampshire indie is a genre that encompasses a wide range of independent music from the state of New Hampshire. It includes everything from indie rock and folk to experimental and electronic music. The music often reflects the state's natural beauty and rural character, and is known for its introspective lyrics and DIY ethos. Many New Hampshire indie bands have gained national recognition in recent years.
